[{"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "480918507", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": true, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "大部分这样不怕死的人真的是命比较不值钱，凡是命值钱的人都不会这么不守交规，毕竟那些不怕死的人没有受过多少安全教育。", "like_count": 698, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "489246979", "reply_comment_id": "489239386", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "哈哈，毕竟死了就是80万，有些人一辈子都存不下80万呢（滑稽脸）", "like_count": 119, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhi-shi-chan-quan-bao-hu-san", "headline": "美食", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "489239386", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我骑两轮和你四轮的对肝  ，可能你血赚，但我完全不亏。（滑稽脸）", "like_count": 60, "author_name": "反面角色", "author_id": "b5ec3848c12643154622e2b18f66d19f", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "491547121", "reply_comment_id": "491527510", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是的，我小时候也是不怕死，因为好玩，骑着自行车到处逆行，晚上骑车也没有灯。长大以后自己开车了就知道了，如果出点什么意外，断胳膊断腿都是小事。。<br>而且我还在一个沿海省会，这里竟然有166万登记在册的电动车，还有很多超标车，相比之下才80万的机动车。基本上电动车都占用了非机动车道+最右侧机动车道，占用两条机动车道都是常有的。<br>闯红灯（非常多）、机动车道内最左侧逆行、超速、超标，在机动车流里蛇皮走位的不计其数，甚至刮蹭了机动车也是直接逃逸。<br>他们完全就是抱着你们不敢撞我，撞了我也有钱拿的态度，死命的作死。只能希望有生之年交规可以健全吧。", "like_count": 17, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-mu-cheng-quan", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "545374254", "reply_comment_id": "489239386", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>你当然亏，在路上规规矩矩的开车，突然就要陪人家几十万，搞不好车也没了，这还不亏？</p>", "like_count": 6, "author_name": "知乎用户Bao5Er", "author_id": "1665cea3864c0c3dbf13631870ed9c54", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhao-yong-chao-80-81", "headline": "一句话", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "535658205", "reply_comment_id": "491547121", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>唉，反正之前骑自行车就特别害怕开电动车的，现在开车更是怕的要死。</p>", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "粑粑喷射", "author_id": "8a904bf83a8c2aa7176cd5c3a63cf780", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhao-yong-chao-80-81", "headline": "一句话", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "491527510", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "为了节省一分钟的时间冒生命危险闯红灯……也是算不清自己命值多少钱的。", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "粑粑喷射", "author_id": "8a904bf83a8c2aa7176cd5c3a63cf780", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xia-tian-29-90-75", "headline": "通信狗", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "490118088", "reply_comment_id": "489239386", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对的，活着血赚，死了不亏", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "夏天", "author_id": "ff5604ecaf024fc0bcd9ba1d52b77e6d", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "631114105", "reply_comment_id": "631095073", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我有两次真的是下雨天被A柱盲区吓得不轻，完全没有想到会有小孩子横穿马路，还好我速度慢，才20多，看到他赶紧刹停了。第二次是在郊区，没有路灯只有红绿灯，有人闯红灯，再加上我男友喝醉了，的确精神没有太集中，开过斑马线以后才发现竟然有人站在我窗边，我完全没看到，想想真的后怕，不过还好车速也慢，30左右。<br>我的车A柱盲区还特别大……车窗贴膜也比较黑，有时候下雨真的很无奈。<br>还有前几天看到前车不小心别了一下闯红灯的电动车，他们两个对骂了一路。我真的不懂，那些不守交规的人真的就觉得机动车一定会让他们吗？很多时候真的不是不让，而是根本看不见。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-xia-94-75", "headline": "颓废", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "638325969", "reply_comment_id": "630957318", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我没有电瓶车，我骑自行车没有办法必须借道机动车道的时候，都会先回头观察后方是否有车。但是大多电瓶车，速度又快，又不看路况，随意变道，吓死人。我开车时候常说他们的后视镜是用来出气的…甚至很多自己摘掉了后视镜。唉。一副吃定机动车的嘴脸。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "潇夏", "author_id": "2c7488347de224b2327ea55f1c54b987", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-lu-10-13-64", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "630957318", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>我骑电动车，有时也不得不走机动车道。因为非机动车道经常停满车、被阻挡，甚至根本没有。如果绕道太远，也会短距离逆行。</p><p>有条件的情况下，尽量走非机动车道，尽量靠边走。也不能怪交通部门不作为，往往交通繁忙的地段，车多、人多，没空间把各种车道搞齐全规整。</p><p>我这样怕死的人，也会偶而不守交规。对于那些性子急、没交规意识、没惩罚对应的人的就更加了。有些人在交通繁忙路口，无视红绿灯的存在，看得人胆颤心惊！！</p><p>机动车之所以守交规情况好得多，除了道路设施，跟惩罚执行关系很大。如果没有罚款扣分措施，开汽车的和骑电动车的肯定是一个屌样。</p><p>不管是开汽车还是骑电动车，小心避免被这些人拖累就好了。反正命是自已的！</p>", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "luson", "author_id": "e3e41b5d146895c38943c0f6e197130b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jlyuvictory", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "615810597", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "通过这个过程他们生命价值就变高了，有价了[捂脸][捂脸]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "jlyuvictory", "author_id": "d1dd7f3cffc0ac4204c5b8e2b15f5a72", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xi-gua-ying-yin-shi", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "611289332", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有很多钱人的大多数怕死，没很多钱人受过安全教育也会铤而走险。不同意你的观点，你不用搞两极化。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "心态", "author_id": "23a037c5d9c535e794c7b57665676933", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "bisulong", "headline": "不干法制干宣传的苦逼搬砖狗", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "602720414", "reply_comment_id": "489246979", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>但不是每个有车的能立刻赔付80万哦~</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Ice Cream滴粑粑", "author_id": "3155ea9c3f5c765d0c466173150bca73", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "mr-chimera", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "505542151", "reply_comment_id": "489239386", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "哟，小老板皮的不谈", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Mr.Chimera", "author_id": "081d002c498dc8473a5362544fcaacd7", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "mu-mu-mu-14-61", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4818291028", "reply_comment_id": "490118088", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对，活着不亏，死了血赚[惊喜][惊喜][惊喜]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "木木木", "author_id": "7d0222ddca50c816b3b63ad4ed95dcc9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "946172129", "reply_comment_id": "939458083", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "啥……怎么会不超过30呢？我们二环和快速路限速都是70，照样有人敢横穿马路", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "da-hui-mie-zhe", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "939458083", "reply_comment_id": "480918507", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你错了，正常市里车速都不超过30公里，顶多被碰的摔倒而已，皮肤刮破皮都算严重的了，骨折根本就是中彩票。所以哪有什么不怕死，根本就是脸皮厚也没别的。要是市里速度达到高速一样，你看他们抢个道看看？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "安通彻", "author_id": "882a2b300c934f4bf9d0f55af8e81576", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "936980418", "reply_comment_id": "936583709", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "[飙泪笑]好吧，实在没研究，雷克萨斯那些车我们这里见的最多的就是ES，SUV我就更没研究了，我见识太少了", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xie-kai-28-27", "headline": "软件工程师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "936583709", "reply_comment_id": "936011527", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "卡罗拉，rav4，雷克萨斯NX RX LX这些系列都有啊。。。[捂脸][捂脸]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "英年减肥", "author_id": "587e511a8898050a384ffa0a6fc832d7", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-qian-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "936011527", "reply_comment_id": "935334513", "reply_root_comment_id": "480918507", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "汽车之家上面找了一下……好像丰田就A级车有……我家的凯美瑞也没有[飙泪笑]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "浅浅", "author_id": "f088f6963445aad9add9c7ab931d6080", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "qian-ji-suo", "headline": "唱唱反调", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "480961195", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>机动车胆子大能作死的也不少。</p><p>只不过你开车之后，你居于绝对安全的地位，自然有心思和余力去批评别人的作死行为了。</p>", "like_count": 122, "author_name": "牵机锁", "author_id": "ae345243f92e14066bbb970e34fc4c5a", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "breakrock-28", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "485379238", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "人家开头也说了自己骑车的时候担心自己的安全没有去作死啊。", "like_count": 94, "author_name": "breakrock", "author_id": "14fca5241f8860f50c851ecece1ad2a2", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jumping-wu", "headline": "温故而知新，一个懵懂的产品经理。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "491637336", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "同时开过4轮和2轮，你就知道什么叫惜命了。", "like_count": 15, "author_name": "Juwwwww", "author_id": "6d7eb565fd6c33e065ddef4d02721590", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhe-jiang-wu-yan-zu-xxd", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "506799638", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这么说吧...以前骑车骑电驴傍晚太阳刚落山的时候懒得开灯，开过汽车后发现这种时候电驴不开灯在路口处压根注意不到！遇到过几次真的是冷汗直流，之后只要天色暗下来就开灯", "like_count": 13, "author_name": "Clzzz", "author_id": "702070e7a775d44f9dc0980d779831f2", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "player2", "headline": "一个臭打游戏的。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "676232095", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "绝对安全地位就有心思和余力了？有一次我在右拐专用车道碰到一个突然蹿出来的女士摩托车，要不是我反应快打了一把方向盘这阿姨肯定飞出去了，老子摇下车窗就是一顿骂。我怕的不是她被我撞死，我怕的是撞死之后我要负责，要花时间处理这些麻烦事。至于别人怎么作死我真的一点都不关心，只要不到我面前作死就行了。我自己骑电动车的时候规规矩矩，从来不在机动车道上扭来扭去。", "like_count": 7, "author_name": "断指轩辕佛罗多", "author_id": "23b191c114edeb869cd0c3b1b79f00c1", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wei-guan-cou-re-nao", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "630127080", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是否恶意引导对立？", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "围观凑热闹", "author_id": "2e340490923863a8af6d37d29e9788d1", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yang-mou-ren-12", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "490653057", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "寻死怎么办", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "谓我何求", "author_id": "f3d7365f8f53b297dbca18d9eb3f45f5", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shi-shu-qing-hua", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "817009698", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "唱唱反调？你个小闺女挺调皮来", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "诗书青华", "author_id": "145048419678fd18628999499bd5ea14", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "qian-jiang-yue-15-23", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "787109240", "reply_comment_id": "480961195", "reply_root_comment_id": "480961195", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "所以我三者都是最少买够100万，我开车遵守交通规则，但不能保证骑车的也遵守。万一哪个不看路的或者寻死的自己撞上来，就算JJ和稀泥给我弄个次责，可能都要赔不少钱。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户1fKAa3", "author_id": "a6c3200f0b222cb8ac1de6e246a3c40c", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "yi-da-li-pao-89", "headline": "汽车", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481322803", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "481322803", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>反正我自己开车以后，有时出去骑摩拜会很注意交通规则，有自行车车道走自行车道，没有尽量靠右，红绿灯路口也会等着，停放在不影响小车行驶的地方。步行过马路走斑马线，有红绿灯就等着，没有如果小车让行，我就快走几步，绝对不会磨磨蹭蹭像逛街似的慢慢走，因为我知道小车不停的等也会很烦心。也绝对不会突然从某个地方闯到马路，因为我知道开车会有视角盲区。</p><p>反正我自己开车，知道什么行为会带来危险，尽量让自己和身边的人不那么去做，换位思考很重要。不要觉得自己没开车是弱势群体就为所欲为，身体是自己的，命也是自己的。</p>", "like_count": 67, "author_name": "意大利炮", "author_id": "a556aac2d9eff5dfd858638c2301363c", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "niu-kun-98-26", "headline": "暴雪一生黑", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481337860", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337860", "hot": false, "is_author": fals