e, "comment_id": "534739746", "reply_comment_id": "481298417", "reply_root_comment_id": "481298417", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>非机动车道上全是人，人行道上全是停着的汽车！</p>", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "织影者丶审判", "author_id": "1e9798f13aa285af529e431be47fcbcd", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lu-feng-23-44", "headline": "it爱好", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "488240641", "reply_comment_id": "481298417", "reply_root_comment_id": "481298417", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没开车之前 我认为车不敢撞我 有了车以后 我不敢把自己的命寄托在人家的脚下", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "龙与地下城", "author_id": "2c2aab7dcdbaee83c011a255d4c2fdb8", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lm-wow-19-91", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481301813", "reply_comment_id": "481298417", "reply_root_comment_id": "481298417", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "厉害", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "知乎用户431hYZ", "author_id": "e82a9daabde56e72273a73b889a86581", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "longway771", "headline": "big brother is watching you.", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4795993337", "reply_comment_id": "481298417", "reply_root_comment_id": "481298417", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "出事故受害者能赢得钱？ 想多了吧。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "longway", "author_id": "f8b1ba700114d3e0ef1aa1ae2edf18cb", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "liu-can-15", "headline": "做人工智能的蠢货", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481337503", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>都是相对的，目前骑电驴上下班，有些车主真的贱，非得走非机动车道，上次有个傻逼车主右转，前面直行红灯，一把方向直接闯进非机动道，我立马捏死刹车，要不然，右边非得给他刮花。</p>", "like_count": 43, "author_name": "这样就认不出我了", "author_id": "e4554cfac08be2c8d67372b98ce27310", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "zhang-chi-69-87", "headline": "希望若干年后，我还是我。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "483550620", "reply_comment_id": "481337503", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": true, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我有次在非机动车道上骑车，后面就上来一辆机动车。先说明一下，那个路段是个铁道桥，机动车道在下层，非机动车道在上层，没有路内停车位，也没有其他叉路口。如果想开到对方车道就得从一开始就开进去。然后那个车从老远就开始一直按喇叭(我们城市禁止按喇叭)，也没减速直到离我很近了才一脚急刹车停下，然后摇下车窗开骂。我也没惯病，把车在马路中间一横，开始给交警打电话。打了三次电话，大概过了半小时，交警来了。问了下情况，和我说，那你让一下吧。当时我这个气啊，就和交警说，我让路可以，但是对方未按指定车道行驶，你既不纠正错误，也不对违法行为进行处罚，我一定会投诉你的。然后那个警察非常无奈又意味深长的看了我几秒，给对方开了罚单，又指挥对方倒了回去走机动车道。", "like_count": 163, "author_name": "张驰", "author_id": "115570da11ebd6d40a8521553af51111", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-can-15", "headline": "做人工智能的蠢货", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "483561012", "reply_comment_id": "483550620", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>干得漂亮，这种人就欠收拾，交警也是够水的</p>", "like_count": 33, "author_name": "这样就认不出我了", "author_id": "e4554cfac08be2c8d67372b98ce27310", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wu-xing-shang-jiang-49", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "491321092", "reply_comment_id": "481337503", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "遵守交规的人，不管是开车还是骑车都会遵守，不遵守的人，不管是开车还是骑车都不会遵守！跟交通方式无关，跟人有关！", "like_count": 22, "author_name": "五星上将", "author_id": "5ee9ebafffd8b363cbd56d6d92223e89", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xing-dong-64-75-32", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "488725235", "reply_comment_id": "481337503", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "说的对，但是机动车跑到非机动车道的比例可是比非机动车跑到机动车道的比例要小太多。而且，机动车跑到非机动车道上可能会被罚款、贴罚单什么的，但是非机动车跑到机动车道上呢？啥事也没有，所以这就造成了绝大多数非机动车目无交通法规，骑着车乱窜！", "like_count": 19, "author_name": "行冬", "author_id": "8dcd1a02bd0a92d4678e9305f44f8a77", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "y