nonymous": false}, {"url_token": "chmod_777", "headline": "当变革之风吹起时，一些人筑起围墙，另一些人则建造风车", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "495276117", "reply_comment_id": "488725235", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你应该这样想，要么啥事没有，要么一命呜呼了，这样想是不是心里好受多了呢", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "chmod 777", "author_id": "ad324ff4476c5ffea9fdde0b7680a644", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wang-chang-ge-67", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2075418239", "reply_comment_id": "488725235", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>很多时候非机动车是被逼走机动车道的，非机动车道被机动车堵了，全是停车的和四个轮子在开的，根本过不了你让人家在天上飞呀，不要说小地方，就杭州</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云间白鹿", "author_id": "7960e4c5ca6d0b5685fc30cd9a23ee13", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shu-zhu-zi-32", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1053590156", "reply_comment_id": "486980813", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "因为全天都堵车。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "糖醋烧饼", "author_id": "14f9f8096311da772785c108e3bbbb16", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "weng-lei-51-79", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "851558341", "reply_comment_id": "483550620", "reply_root_comment_id": "481337503", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "要是，违法非机动车也采取用分制，需要考取驾照，该多好。[捂脸]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户BmBbuo", "author_id": "66fcf2cad13adb56ce9cc9f5c02baf86", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "wei-hu-62-60", "headline": "发呆", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481906323", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "考了科目一之后，我觉得国家有必要从小学开始，对所有的人进行这类的教育。<br>不能总是一味的指望车让人，因为有许多人是真的不懂交通法规的。他们在马路上的随意性对自己对别人也是不负责的。<br>车祸频发，希望大家无论是司机还是行人都遵守交通法规，注意安全，不要争分夺秒！", "like_count": 33, "author_name": "尾狐", "author_id": "8719923fdadd339a8ca40ad3256ed294", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "wu-yang-tian-di", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "643931230", "reply_comment_id": "481906323", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我小时候（70年代），骑自行车过红绿灯路口下车推行、后座不准带人、不得逆行，发现了轻则教育或充当临时街头宣传协管，只到抓住下一个，重则罚款。那个年代路上机动车非常少，但自行车大军却是规规矩矩。所以我是非常赞同你的建议。交通安全问题和国家采取的措施，包括全民教育、加大法制和惩处力度息息相关。而现在，对行人、非机动车的交通违法行为没有具备警示和禁绝力度的措施，交警对路上横冲直撞的非机动车睁一只眼闭一只眼，更加让这些人觉得没人敢“碰”自己。以上说法还只是表象，要从深层讨论，社会风气、经济环境、政府执政原则乃至国际舆论形势都是影响因素之一。不知道还有没有人记得，上海市实行过一段时间的政策，行人不按交通信号灯通行路口造成交通事故的，机动车无责，俗话就是“撞了白撞”，可后来这个政策取消了。不错，国家在进步，经济民生在发展，人权在加强，可人心却越来越不纯，这时候，就必须依靠各种不断加强和完善的法制法规来约束，有章可循有法可依，不成规矩何来方圆。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "无恙天地", "author_id": "cf688c57271e1d80b84c7b0f1dbe982d", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-cheng-zhi-60-11", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "487043856", "reply_comment_id": "481906323", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "教育都有，所有人都知道红灯停绿灯行，总有人不遵守。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "Laoticle", "author_id": "47207088b990c6650ee5987ebe6e21fb", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-jia-qi-34-88", "headline": "别杠，杠就是你对。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "508550256", "reply_comment_id": "481906323", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没必要，立法谁违章谁全责就成。一味的偏袒所谓弱者，中国特色。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "李嘉琪", "author_id": "4ef084f517b639e46e8b3ac61ae8612e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lm-wow-19-91", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481910322", "reply_comment_id": "481906323", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "唉，是滴呀，这个可以有", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "知乎用户431hYZ", "author_id": "e82a9daabde56e72273a73b889a86581", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "de-ke-si-te-5", "headline": "带有嘲讽技能的比喻狂魔", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "800803302", "reply_comment_id": "481906323", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>自从学车后，过马路更加怂了，因为我知道，车子不是说刹停就刹停的。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "北极熊猫", "author_id": "e5e8489cbb3b1dc5af7119db3387ba87", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "rubyhui-tu", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "659515143", "reply_comment_id": "508550256", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "也没有一味偏袒，上周有交警来我们公司讲课（工作要求每年学习一次），讲了一个案例，在没有红绿灯的十字路口，小汽车正常直行，助力车正常直行，然后相撞。最后判定的是助力车全责，理由是第一小汽车车速很慢，第二助力车连非机动车都算不上，没有道具使用权，也就是说这种车不允许上路。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "RUBY灰兔", "author_id": "b188fc1e804a6c0f6bd7e7a87cda9fd6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wu-yang-tian-di", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "643940855", "reply_comment_id": "487043856", "reply_root_comment_id": "481906323", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "犯错成本太低自然没人遵守。机动车驾驶员好歹经过培训通过考试，有车以后爱惜得不得了。车自然好管，罚。人，怎么管，罚多了人耍赖，罚少了不值得。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "无恙天地", "author_id": "cf688c57271e1d80b84c7b0f1dbe982d", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "cheng-fa-zhe-36", "headline": "有些事情一转身就是一辈子", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "481388795", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "481388795", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>前几天开车十字路口等红绿等，眼阵阵看着一无牌摩托车逆行，闯红灯，还是单手握把，右手操作手机，直直冲出来，把一俩绿灯正常左拐的小车吓的半死，急刹停原地楞了十几秒没动一下，摩托边玩手机边开就那么走了。。。</p>", "like_count": 28, "author_name": "一转身一辈子", "author_id": "d326b35cc30717c177221945b74f52ac", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ge-ge-ge-ge-ge-64-11", 